'''Emmon Cuy''' is a member of [[Renly Baratheon]]'s [[Kingsguard]]. He is a background character in the [[Season 2|second season]], played by an unidentified extra and only appears in the &quot;[[The Ghost of Harrenhal]]&quot;. Ser Emmon is killed by [[Brienne]] of Tarth after he blames and attacks her in the wake of Renly's assassination.
